channel.title: First Apostolic Church Knoxville Audio Podcast
channel.description: Live Worship Services from First Apostolic Church Knoxville Tennessee, Bishop Billy McCool and Pastor Mark McCool. We are seeing a wonderful move of the Spirit at FAC Knoxville and hope you will join us for worship services soon. We know you will find our people are friendly, our services are filled with praise and worship, and that God is moving among us in a beautiful way.
